to finish the report earlier.
要我提前把报告做完

1876
02:33:36,666 --> 02:33:39,333
A lotta money,
how much are we talking about? 
一大笔钱，是多大笔？

1877
02:33:40,416 --> 02:33:41,750
100,000 euros.
10万欧元

1878
02:33:42,916 --> 02:33:44,666
100,000 euros?
10万欧元?

1879
02:33:45,166 --> 02:33:47,666
100,000 euros?
-Yes.
10万欧元? -对

1880
02:33:51,416 --> 02:33:56,333
I never thought you'd be worth so much.
没想到你这么值钱

1881
02:33:56,500 --> 02:33:58,083
100,000 euros?
10万欧元?

1882
02:33:58,166 --> 02:34:00,916
He offered me 150,000 euros.
他给我开了15万欧元

1883
02:34:01,083 --> 02:34:04,583
Sorry, I'm still thinking
about the 100,000!
抱歉 我还在想那10万欧元

1884
02:34:05,083 --> 02:34:06,000
Damn!
天啊

1885
02:34:07,833 --> 02:34:11,583
He says construction must begin
before the rainy season.
他说雨季前必须开工

1886
02:34:11,666 --> 02:34:13,416
He's in a hurry.
他很急

1887
02:34:14,166 --> 02:34:15,916
What did you say?
你怎么说?

1888
02:34:17,916 --> 02:34:19,583
I said no, obviously.
当然是拒绝

1889
02:34:20,833 --> 02:34:23,000
- Obviously
- It's insulting
-当然-这太侮辱人了

1890
02:34:23,166 --> 02:34:24,000
Insulting.…
侮辱

1891
02:34:24,166 --> 02:34:28,416
But weren't you almost done
with the report?
但你的报告不是快写完了吗?

1892
02:34:29,166 --> 02:34:32,166
-Yes. 
 And from what I gathered,
-是－而且我听说

1893
02:34:33,083 --> 02:34:36,333
firom an ecological point of view
it's beneficial, right?
从生态角度看是有好处的 对吧？

1894
02:34:37,833 --> 02:34:39,833
Ecology can be many things.
 生态这个概念可以

1895
02:34:41,166 --> 02:34:42,416
Like what?
比如呢?

1896
02:34:46,083 --> 02:34:49,916
Are you considering the possibility
I might take that money?
你是觉得我可能会收那笔钱吗?

1897
02:34:51,000 --> 02:34:52,166
No, Sérgio.
不 塞尔吉奥

1898
02:34:52,416 --> 02:34:54,166
I'm trying to figure out
我只是想弄明白

1899
02:34:54,833 --> 02:34:57,833
why you've been offered 150,000 euros.
为什么他们要给你15万欧元

1900
02:34:59,166 --> 02:35:00,666
I told you.
我已经跟你解释过了

1901
02:35:01,083 --> 02:35:05,916
I already have all the data,
but I don't wanna rush it.
而且我手里数据都齐了 但我不想火急火燎的

1902
02:35:06,083 --> 02:35:08,166
I wanna do a good job.
我想做得扎实点

1903
02:35:08,666 --> 02:35:12,083
But if you already have all the data,
既然你数据都齐了

1904
02:35:12,166 --> 02:35:17,333
what's keeping you from finishing
and handing in the report? 
是什么让你还没完成并上交报考呢？

1905
02:35:19,250 --> 02:35:21,916
I wanna follow the right procedure.
因为我要按正确流程来

1906
02:35:22,166 --> 02:35:23,500
And this ain't it.
可这事没那么简单

1907
02:35:24,833 --> 02:35:27,500
Forget it, it was insulting.
Never mind.
算了 刚才太冒犯了 当我没说

1908
02:35:28,416 --> 02:35:30,416
- Insulting?
- Yeah, it disgusts me.
-冒犯？-是的，它让我恶心

1909
02:35:30,833 --> 02:35:31,916
It's disgusting.
太恶心了

1910
02:35:32,666 --> 02:35:33,916
Disgusting?
恶心?

1911
02:35:34,416 --> 02:35:36,500
You know what's disgusting, Sérgio?
恶心？你知道什么才叫恶心吗 塞尔吉奥?

1912
02:35:37,583 --> 02:35:41,666
The power some people have
to say no to 150,000 euros.
是有些人居然能对15万欧元说不

1913
02:35:42,166 --> 02:35:44,833
The importance some people
can give to money,
是有些人能把钱看得那么轻

1914
02:35:45,083 --> 02:35:47,166
that's what's disgusting.
这才是恶心

1915
02:35:51,666 --> 02:35:53,333
It's dirty money.
那是脏钱

1916
02:35:53,833 --> 02:35:55,500
What about the money you earn?
那你赚的钱呢?

1917
02:35:55,666 --> 02:35:58,000
Is your salary clean?
你工资就干净吗?

1918
02:36:06,083 --> 02:36:07,916
You know what's disgusting?
你知道什么才叫恶心吗？

1919
02:36:08,583 --> 02:36:12,250
People being cursed
because of where they were born
有人因为出生地就被诅咒

1920
02:36:12,416 --> 02:36:15,833
and not having their basic needs met.
 连基本需求都满足不了

1921
02:36:16,083 --> 02:36:20,000
It's people like you coming here
and saying no to 150,000 euros.
是像你这样的人来到这儿 还能拒绝15万欧元

1922
02:36:20,250 --> 02:36:21,916
Don't you realize that dirty money
你不明白那是脏钱

1923
02:36:22,083 --> 02:36:24,916
comes from exploiting
these people you're talking about?
那钱来自对那些人的剥削

1924
02:36:25,083 --> 02:36:28,833
And don't you realize
your salary is dirty?
那难道你就不明白 你的工资也是脏的吗?

1925
02:36:30,666 --> 02:36:33,416
That your job is dirty?
你的工作也很脏吗?

1926
02:36:35,583 --> 02:36:40,666
You think the money coming from
 the World Bank and Europe is clean?
你觉得从世界银行和欧洲来的钱就干净吗？

1927
02:36:48,416 --> 02:36:50,833
That's called relieving your conscience,
这叫赎罪感

1928
02:36:50,916 --> 02:36:55,833
something rich people use
to help the poor, those with nothing,
富人用来施舍穷人 那些一无所有的人

1929
02:36:56,083 --> 02:36:58,166
those who need to be helped,
那些需要被帮的人

1930
02:36:58,333 --> 02:37:00,666
incapable of governing themselves.
那些连自己都管不好的人

1931
02:37:00,833 --> 02:37:02,583
And I'm glad we're incapable of that. 
我反而庆幸我们做不到那点

1932
02:37:02,750 --> 02:37:06,916
I'm glad we rely on an outsider
我感到庆幸我们依赖外来者

1933
02:37:07,083 --> 02:37:09,666
to finish a report on a road
来替我们把一条路的报告做完

1934
02:37:09,916 --> 02:37:12,583
and offer him 150,000 euros
然后我们还能给他15万欧元

1935
02:37:12,833 --> 02:37:17,500
so he can have the purity to say no.
让他有说不的纯洁性

1936
02:37:20,416 --> 02:37:22,666
So you'd take the money, is that it?
那你会收钱 是这个意思吗?

1937
02:37:27,833 --> 02:37:29,000
Is that it?
是这样吗?

1938
02:37:29,000 --> 02:37:30,833
Is that it?

1939
02:37:30,833 --> 02:37:34,666
I don't have the power
to say no to 150,000 euros.
我没那个底气对15万欧元说不

1940
02:37:36,916 --> 02:37:38,000
Yet.
现在还没有

1941
02:37:39,916 --> 02:37:41,416
Tell me something then.
那你告诉我

1942
02:37:41,583 --> 02:37:44,750
Imagine you got that money.
What would you do with it?
假如你拿到那笔钱 你会怎么用?

1943
02:37:45,166 --> 02:37:47,416
I think you must ask yourself that.
我觉得你该问问你自己

1944
02:37:48,666 --> 02:37:51,166
If you wanna go to the Maldives...
要是你想去马尔代夫…

1945
02:37:51,500 --> 02:37:53,166
Oh, wait!
哦 等等！

1946
02:37:53,166 --> 02:37:54,833
You'll buy a house for your mom.
你会给你妈买房

1947
02:37:54,916 --> 02:37:59,000
No! 
You'll pay for your nephews' college.
不 你会供你的侄子们上大学

1948
02:37:59,166 --> 02:38:02,083
You'll give it to an orphanage here.
你还会给这儿的孤儿院捐上一笔

1949
02:38:02,666 --> 02:38:07,833
Because you'll want to help,
after everything that's given to you.
因为别人帮过你 你也想帮人

1950
02:38:08,416 --> 02:38:10,250
Ain't that how this works?
不就是这样运作的吗？

1951
02:38:10,916 --> 02:38:15,333
And you'll leave feeling good,
because you helped humanity.
然后你心满意足地走人 觉得自己帮了人类

1952
02:38:20,166 --> 02:38:22,833
Turn right at the end of this road.
到这条路的尽头 右转 

1953
02:38:29,333 --> 02:38:31,333
- Can I park here? 
-Yeah.
-能把车停这儿吗？-可以

1954
