Don't get up, Aunt.
姨 别站起来啦

1966
02:39:08,166 --> 02:39:10,166
How are you?
- I'm okay.
-你怎么样？-我挺好

1967
02:39:10,333 --> 02:39:11,333
How are you? 
你怎么样？

1968
02:39:16,166 --> 02:39:17,583
You look beautiful!
你真漂亮

1969
02:39:19,916 --> 02:39:21,916
Come sit here, Seroio.
- How are you, Uncle?
-塞尔吉奥 来坐这-叔叔 你好吗?

1970
02:39:22,166 --> 02:39:23,916
Look, that's Sérgio.
看 这就是塞尔吉奥

1971
02:39:24,083 --> 02:39:26,250
Your special someone?
- No, he's my friend.
-是你的对象吗？-不是，他只我朋友

1972
02:39:26,416 --> 02:39:27,666
He's not my someone.
他不是我对象

1973
02:39:28,250 --> 02:39:29,583
Where's he gonna sit, Mom?
妈 他坐哪?

1974
02:39:29,750 --> 02:39:31,666
Where can I wash my hands?
我去哪能洗手?

1975
02:39:33,833 --> 02:39:35,250
In the bathroom.
去卫生间

1976
02:39:35,916 --> 02:39:37,666
Show him where to wash his hands.
带他去洗把手

1977
02:39:39,416 --> 02:39:41,666
Can you gimme some...
能给我点…

1978
02:39:53,083 --> 02:39:54,833
There's a sick person in here.
这屋里有个病人

1979
02:39:55,666 --> 02:39:57,750
He's been sick for a long time...
他病很久了

1980
02:39:58,666 --> 02:40:00,250
He can't eat anything.
什么都吃不下

1981
02:40:00,500 --> 02:40:02,166
Throws up everything he eats.
吃什么吐什么

1982
02:40:03,083 --> 02:40:07,500
We must pray for his recovery.
我们得为他祈祷康复

1983
02:40:09,333 --> 02:40:10,416
Come.
来吧

1984
02:40:16,416 --> 02:40:17,916
Bathroom's in there.
卫生间在里面

1985
02:40:19,583 --> 02:40:21,333
Thank you
- You're welcome.
-谢谢 -不客气

1986
02:40:29,333 --> 02:40:31,333
I'm on a diet, but I haven't lost much.
我在减肥，但还没瘦多少呢

1987
