Don't get up,
别起身

1991
02:41:02,500 --> 02:41:03,666
sit down.
坐着

1992
02:41:05,750 --> 02:41:07,166
Are you going to Lisbon?
你要去里斯本吗?

1993
02:41:09,166 --> 02:41:10,166
Are you?
你呢?

1994
02:41:10,333 --> 02:41:11,833
Are you going to Lisbon?
你要去里斯本吗? 

1995
02:41:12,083 --> 02:41:14,333
I want to go too.
Will you take me?
我也想去 你会带我去吗？

1996
02:41:14,500 --> 02:41:15,916
No, we're not gonna take you.
不 我们不带你去

1997
