Uncle!
叔叔

2002
02:41:27,333 --> 02:41:30,416
He's a guest! Sérgio's a guest!
他是客人 塞尔吉奥是客人

2003
02:41:30,583 --> 02:41:33,333
So tell him, he'll understand.
那就跟他说一下，他就懂了

2004
02:41:33,666 --> 02:41:36,916
Pecixe is the island
of the Manjak people.
佩希谢是曼雅克人的岛

2005
02:41:37,333 --> 02:41:38,583
In the north?
在北边吗?

2006
02:41:38,833 --> 02:41:40,166
Yeah, up north.
对在北边

2007
