Let's see if we have enough.
我看看够不够

2021
02:42:15,416 --> 02:42:17,333
One for each.
一人一瓶

2022
02:42:20,416 --> 02:42:21,666
Just a minute.
等一下

2023
02:42:24,333 --> 02:42:25,250
Sérgio.
塞尔吉奥

2024
02:42:26,833 --> 02:42:28,000
Sorry.
抱歉

2025
02:42:29,750 --> 02:42:30,833
Juice?
果汁?

2026
02:42:32,000 --> 02:42:35,250
Are you worried about your diet
-I can have lunch now.
你还担心身材吗？-我现在能吃午饭了

