Sérgio, thank you so much!

2029
02:42:47,166 --> 02:42:48,833
Thank you for what?

2030
02:42:49,083 --> 02:42:50,666
For his visit!
谢谢他的来访

2031
02:42:50,916 --> 02:42:52,333
Diára's here!

2032
02:42:53,333 --> 02:42:54,666
Do I look good?
我戴着好看吗?

2033
02:42:56,833 --> 02:42:58,250
Only if you wear a diadem.

2034
02:42:58,416 --> 02:43:01,916
We're almost a family.
我们差不多是一家子了

2035
02:43:02,166 --> 02:43:05,500
We're almosta
- A family? Where?
-我们差不多是一家子了-一家子？在哪?

2036
02:43:18,000 --> 02:43:19,083
Diára.
迪娅拉

2037
02:43:23,083 --> 02:43:24,333
Wake up.
醒醒

2038
02:43:24,750 --> 02:43:26,250
We're here.
到了

2039
02:43:28,083 --> 02:43:29,416
We're here.
我们到了

2040
02:43:53,500 --> 02:43:55,583
Can you still climb stairs?
你还能爬楼梯吗?

2041
02:43:55,666 --> 02:43:57,000
Your hair!
你的头发

2042
02:44:17,833 --> 02:44:18,916
Sérgio!
塞尔吉奥

2043
