I think I'm gonna go.
我想我得走了

2044
02:44:24,833 --> 02:44:26,666
You're gonna go? Why?
你要走吗为什么?

2045
02:44:26,833 --> 02:44:28,166
I'm tired.
我累了

2046
02:44:28,500 --> 02:44:29,500
Come in.
来吧

2047
02:44:30,416 --> 02:44:31,250
No
Please.
-不要-求你了

2048
02:44:32,666 --> 02:44:34,750
I'm tired, I'm sleepy.
我累了也困了

2049
02:44:35,500 --> 02:44:37,583
Didn't you wanna meet my family?
你不是想见见我家吗

2050
02:44:37,750 --> 02:44:40,750
Didn't you say you wanted
to know everything about me?
你不是说想把我都了解透吗?

2051
02:44:42,666 --> 02:44:43,500
Well?
所以?

2052
02:44:43,500 --> 02:44:43,916
Well?

2053
02:44:43,916 --> 02:44:45,000
It's done.
心愿完成了

2054
02:44:47,333 --> 02:44:49,000
Family lunch.

2055
02:44:53,416 --> 02:44:55,416
What are you doing tomorrow?
你明天干嘛?

2056
02:44:58,000 --> 02:44:58,916
Nothing
没事

2057
02:45:00,333 --> 02:45:02,166
I'm gonna hang out with Jota.
我去和若塔混

2058
02:45:03,083 --> 02:45:05,416
Maybe he'll stay over.
他可能会住一晚

2059
02:45:06,250 --> 02:45:08,083
And you could come with us.
你也可以一起来

2060
02:45:09,416 --> 02:45:10,750
Do you wanna come?

2061
02:45:11,916 --> 02:45:13,416
Yeah.
想

2062
02:45:13,416 --> 02:45:14,833
Yeah?
- Cool.

2063
02:45:15,916 --> 02:45:18,416
And I would really like it
我也很想

2064
02:45:19,166 --> 02:45:22,333
if you sat down and watched.
你能坐着看

2065
02:45:24,583 --> 02:45:25,916
Huh?
啊？

2066
02:45:25,916 --> 02:45:27,333
I would really like it
